query:
SELECT 
    i.id,
    i.name,
    i.unit,
    i.costPerUnit,
    ic.fromUnit,
    ic.toUnit,
    ic.conversionFactor
FROM ingredients i
LEFT JOIN ingredientConversions ic ON i.id = ic.ingredientId
WHERE i.name LIKE '%Scallops%';
